data.description: Gorgeous, updated home in the newer area of Sun River. This impeccable home has hardwood flooring throughout, plantation shutters, custom valences & built-ins, and ALL new appliances! NEW hot water heater also. Not one detail overlooked. 3rd car garage has a mini-split system for temp control, lots of storage, great project space. Front yard: enclosed pony wall for patio space. Backyard: tranquil fountain year round, covered patio, fully fenced in. Make this your get-away home now! Move-in ready.
